OL,10,GOur modern sewage system relies on
OL,11,Gvast amounts of water and this causes
OL,12,Ghuge problems. Perhaps the greatest
OL,13,Gbeing that the anaerobic microbes that
OL,14,Gbreak down human waste in water are
OL,15,Ginefficient, produce greenhouse gases,
OL,16,Gand then waste ends up in the rivers
OL,17,Gand seas producing algal blooms and
OL,18,Gfoul smells. Whereas their descendants
OL,19,Gon land (aerobic microbes) are
OL,20,Gextremely efficient and only produce
